dublin_core.dcvalue: The mission of University of Iowa Health Care simply stated is Changing Medicine Changing Lives And in Iowa a predominantly rural state with an aging population changing medicine to improve the lives of all Iowans means identifying new opportunities for the delivery of world class medical care beyond our Iowa City campus Enter Ul Health Care s eHealth and eNovation Center a pioneering telemedicine initiative founded in 2013 that links rural hospitals and physicians in Iowa with specialists at University of Iowa Hospitals and Clinics UIHC in real time
Iowa medicine : journal of the Iowa Medical Society
